ClickHouse increase ReadBufferFromFileDescriptorReadFailed or ReadBufferFromFileDescriptorReadFailed in `system.events` table.
It mean the read (read/pread) or writes (write/pwrite) to a file descriptor. Does not include sockets.
System can't read or write to some files.
Please check [logs](/#/components/{{ componentUrnForUrl }}#logs) of the pod.